summary: By Brian Cantor - Headline Planet   Buoyed by critical acclaim, strong listener callouts and solid sales numbers, Taylor Swift’s...
caption:
By Brian Cantor - Headline Planet 

 Buoyed by critical acclaim, strong listener callouts and solid sales numbers, Taylor Swift’s “Delicate” continues its climb at hot adult contemporary radio. Up three places, the “reputation” track earns #3 on this week’s edition of the Mediabase hot adult contemporary radio chart. 

 “Delicate” received 5,683 spins during the June 17-23 tracking period. This week’s count tops last week’s mark by 556 spins. 

 Only one song — Maroon 5’s “Girls Like You (featuring Cardi B)” — enjoyed a greater airplay gain this week. 

 “Delicate” concurrently rises to #8 at pop radio, while holding at #9 on the adult contemporary chart.
